## Quick Reference

```bash
# Start of every session
git status                        # see what's changed
git pull origin dev               # sync if working across machines

# Stage and commit
git add .
git commit -m "stage: description"
git push origin dev

# Merge to main when stage is verified
git checkout main
git merge dev
git push origin main

# Check history
git log --oneline
```
